<% content_for :title, "Pagecord Privacy Policy" %>

<div class="prose dark:prose-invert mb-12 px-4">
  <h2 class="source-serif font-semibold tracking-tight text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>Pagecord ("we") is committed to protecting your privacy in compliance with the UK GDPR.</p>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">1. Data Controller</h3>
  <p>The Data Controller is Pagecord. Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@pagecord.com">hello@pagecord.com</a>.</p>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">2. Lawful Basis for Processing</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account Data (Email/Name):</strong> Processed under <em>Contractual Necessity</em> to provide the service.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Data (IPs/Logs):</strong> Processed under <em>Legitimate Interests</em> to prevent fraud and abuse.</li>
    <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> Processed only with your <em>Consent</em>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">3. Sub-Processors & International Transfers</h3>
  <p>We use the following third parties to run Pagecord. Some may process data outside the UK/EEA (e.g., USA). Where this occurs, we ensure Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) are in place:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Paddle:</strong> Payments & Billing</li>
    <li><strong>Hetzner:</strong> Server Infrastructure (Germany)</li>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare / R2:</strong> Security & Image Storage</li>
    <li><strong>Postmark / Mailpace:</strong> Transactional Emails</li>
    <li><strong>AppSignal / Sentry:</strong> Error Monitoring</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">4. Retention & Cookies</h3>
  <p><strong>Retention:</strong> We keep account data for as long as your account is active. Upon deletion, data is removed from active databases within 30 days. Billing records are kept for 6 years as required by UK tax law.</p>
  <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use essential cookies to maintain your session and security. We do not use third-party tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">5. Children's Privacy</h3>
  <p>Pagecord does not knowingly collect data from children under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@pagecord.com">hello@pagecord.com</a> for immediate deletion.</p>

  <h3 class="source-serif font-semibold text-2xl">6. Your Rights</h3>
  <p>Under the UK GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, or port your data. You may also object to or restrict processing. To exercise these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@pagecord.com">hello@pagecord.com</a>. You may lodge a complaint with the <a href="https://ico.org.uk/">ICO</a> if you feel your data is mishandled.</p>

  <p class="text-sm italic">Last updated: January 2026</p>
